file.name: query_expected.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Entities
  version: "1.0"
servers:
  - url: /
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: getRoot
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: query
          required: true
          style: form
          explode: true
          schema:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Id"
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Person"
components:
  schemas:
    Person:
      required:
        - age
        - name
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        age:
          minimum: 11
          type: integer
    Id:
      type: string
      enum:
        - a
        - b
